  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >L is a wandering knight, driven by a deep desire to discover his true self and the reason for his existence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>The Darkblade</strong>, you follow L's journey across the land — meeting friends, allies, rivals, enemies, and uncovering hidden truths along the way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slay Monsters with Souls-like Experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrading Skills, Equipment and Dark Core.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventuring across the land to find the truth.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bringing pet with in adventure.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >L is a wandering knight, driven by a deep desire to discover his true self and the reason for his existence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>The Darkblade</strong>, you follow L's journey across the land — meeting friends, allies, rivals, enemies, and uncovering hidden truths along the way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slay Monsters with Souls-like Experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrading Skills, Equipment and Dark Core.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adventuring across the land to find the truth.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bringing pet with in adventure.</p></li></ul>",
